<% content_for :title, "COVID-19 Instructions — AACT" %>

<div class="mb-6">
  <%= render "shared/back_link", path: snapshots_path, label: "Snapshots" %>
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-2">COVID-19 Spreadsheet Instructions</h1>
</div>

<div class="max-w-3xl space-y-8">
  <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-200 rounded-lg p-4">
    <p class="text-sm text-yellow-800">
      <strong>Please Note:</strong> COVID-19 spreadsheets are no longer actively generated. Check the
      "Last Exported" date on the snapshots page for the most recent available data.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Overview</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">
      These files contain clinical studies related to <strong>COVID-19</strong> from ClinicalTrials.gov as of
      the date of file creation. Each file allows users without advanced database skills to explore trials in
      spreadsheet format.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">
      The spreadsheets were created using
      <a href="https://clinicaltrials.gov/search?cond=COVID-19" class="text-blue hover:underline" target="_blank">ClinicalTrials.gov's COVID-19 search criteria</a>
      and the AACT database. Each study appears as a single row with 68 columns of information.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
      For current COVID-19 clinical trial information, visit
      <a href="https://clinicaltrials.gov/search?cond=COVID-19" class="text-blue hover:underline" target="_blank">ClinicalTrials.gov</a> directly.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-6">Steps</h2>
    <ol class="space-y-6">
      <li class="flex gap-4">
        <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-navy text-white text-sm font-bold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">1</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-1">Download a COVID-19 spreadsheet</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
            Browse available files on the
            <%= link_to "COVID-19 archive page", archive_snapshots_path(type: "covid"), class: "text-blue hover:underline" %>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>

      <li class="flex gap-4">
        <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-navy text-white text-sm font-bold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">2</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-1">Open with spreadsheet software</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
            Open the downloaded file in <strong>Microsoft Excel, Google Sheets, or LibreOffice Calc</strong>.
            Each row represents one clinical trial, with columns for study identifiers, titles, conditions,
            interventions, locations, and results status.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</div>
